ame": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 428156, "username": "fbu11", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/fbu11", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/01ae/05cd/428156_mini.png?m=1781319873", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/01ae/05cd/428156_normal.png?m=1781319873", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/01ae/05cd/428156_large.png?m=1781319873", "created": 1562666139, "last_modified": 1781319873, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "isbase", "last_touched": 1783790165, "title": "GPT5.6 SOL 也就那么回事", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1226536", "created": 1783737842, "deleted": 0, "content": "试了新的 5.6 的 SOL 发现也就呢样，做不到的还是做不到，就是 codex 看上去比之前花哨了点，整体上还是不如 Fable 5,只能期待下后续可能的 GPT 6 ，ai 的这些小版本更新没什么大的进步，只能等大版本了", "content_rendered": "<p>试了新的 5.6 的 SOL 发现也就呢样，做不到的还是做不到，就是 codex 看上去比之前花哨了点，整体上还是不如 Fable 5,只能期待下后续可能的 GPT 6 ，ai 的这些小版本更新没什么大的进步，只能等大版本了</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783737842, "replies": 33, "id": 1226536}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23827, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3707, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 482248, "username": "ximaoyang", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ximaoyang", "website": "https://codeplato3721.github.io/", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "代码Plato", "bio": "怎么才能改自己的用户名啊。。。", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c764/a00c/482248_mini.png?m=1779329638", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c764/a00c/482248_normal.png?m=1779329638", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c764/a00c/482248_large.png?m=1779329638", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c764/a00c/482248_xlarge.png?m=1779329638", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c764/a00c/482248_xxlarge.png?m=1779329638", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c764/a00c/482248_xxxlarge.png?m=1779329638", "created": 1586271105, "last_modified": 1779329638, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "osto", "last_touched": 1783785261, "title": "用了 ai 之后工作很碎片化，完全无法进入心流", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1226513", "created": 1783713428, "deleted": 0, "content": "有没有发现用了 ai 之后，工作时间高度碎片化。在等待 ai 写代码的时候我去做别的事情，或者别的项目，这让我感觉很糟糕，完全无法进入心流状态。\r\n整个人过的浑浑噩噩，慌慌张张，经常忘记 agent 事情做完了，顾了这个顾不了那个。导致事情做的更慢\r\n\r\n有什么好的办法吗？你们在等 ai 工作的时候会干啥？还是因为怕自己没了状态就什么都不干盯着 ai 看？", "content_rendered": "<p>有没有发现用了 ai 之后，工作时间高度碎片化。在等待 ai 写代码的时候我去做别的事情，或者别的项目，这让我感觉很糟糕，完全无法进入心流状态。\n整个人过的浑浑噩噩，慌慌张张，经常忘记 agent 事情做完了，顾了这个顾不了那个。导致事情做的更慢</p>\n<p>有什么好的办法吗？你们在等 ai 工作的时候会干啥？还是因为怕自己没了状态就什么都不干盯着 ai 看？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783769515, "replies": 23, "id": 1226513}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e4da/3b7f/5_large.png?m=1584385880", "name": "movie", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e4da/3b7f/5_normal.png?m=1584385880", "title": "电影", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/movie", "topics": 1510, "footer": "", "header": "用 90 分钟去体验另外一个世界。", "title_alternative": "Movie", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e4da/3b7f/5_mini.png?m=1584385880", "stars": 2179, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 5, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 609073, "username": "jackenliu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jackenliu", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d0ad597cd5579b27faa8c2aa2a2222de?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d0ad597cd5579b27faa8c2aa2a2222de?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_l